Introduction

WJMK (우주미키) is a four-member special project unit group created by Starship Entertainment and Fantagio Music. The unit consists of WJSN's Seola and Luda, and Weki Meki's Yoojung and Doyeon. They debuted on June 1, 2018 with the single "Strong".
